features:
The popular Padrone, now with multi-sensor and data upload capacity
Bluetooth Smart compatible (sensors & connectivity)
ISC-12 dual speed/cadence sensor included
Heart rate (optional, with HR-12 or other Bluetooth monitor)
Super easy setup, can be done directly on the unit or using a smart phone
Large 32x43mm & customizeable 3-rows display
Automatic 2nd bike recognition
Sensor battery alarm
ClicTec interface
Upload ride summaries to Strava and TrainingPeaks via CatEye cycling app
